# Draft:Stewart Keller

Stewart Keller (born September 9, 1997), is an American composer and musician. Keller has scored several notable indie games such as Everhood 2 and Juice Galaxy. He has collaborated with notable artists such as Waterflame, Josh Mancell, David Firth, and LumpyTouch.
Keller has also released a large handful of albums on cassette, CD, and floppy disc on Bandcamp.
